<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-12-15T03:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-12-15T03:00:00-05:00" n="590" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d590">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">740.0011 European War 1939/26496:
                            Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Consul tit Aden (<persName type="from">Timberlake</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                    State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Aden</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-12-15T11:00:00+03:00">December
                                    15, 1942—11 a.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received 11:45 a.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>50. Reference my telegram No. 49, December 10. It is now an important
                            factor since Platt telegraphed today he will send his proposal to Dupont
                            direct unless I am as he hopes instructed by tonight to deliver them by
                            tonight. I think I have stalled him until tomorrow night. For many
                            reasons I believe it of great importance in securing voluntary
                            cooperation of French that I take in proposal and urgently request
                            Department instruct me as suggested last paragraph my telegram No.
                            [48].</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Timberlake</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>